---
---

<section id="cli" class="section">
  <div class="container cli-layout">

    <div class="cli-text">
      <div class="eyebrow">Keel CLI</div>
      <h2>De cero a API<br /><span class="accent-blue">en segundos</span></h2>
      <p class="cli-desc">
        Scaffolding de proyectos, generación de módulos, controladores, servicios,
        repositorios y guardas. Un comando y tienes la estructura lista.
      </p>

      <ul class="cli-feature-list">
        <li>
          <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/>
          </svg>
          Proyecto completo con un solo comando
        </li>
        <li>
          <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/>
          </svg>
          Generación de cualquier capa de forma independiente
        </li>
        <li>
          <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/>
          </svg>
          Servidor de desarrollo con live reload (<code>keel run</code>)
        </li>
        <li>
          <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/>
          </svg>
          Auto-actualización con <code>keel upgrade</code>
        </li>
      </ul>

      <a href="https://docs.keel-go.dev" class="btn-cli">
        Ver documentación del CLI →
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="terminal">
      <div class="terminal-bar">
        <span class="dot red"></span>
        <span class="dot yellow"></span>
        <span class="dot green"></span>
        <span class="terminal-title">terminal</span>
      </div>
      <div class="terminal-body">
        <div class="t-line">
          <span class="prompt">$</span>
          <span class="cmd">keel new my-api</span>
        </div>
        <div class="t-output">✓ Proyecto creado en ./my-api</div>
        <div class="t-output">✓ go.mod inicializado</div>
        <div class="t-output">✓ .env configurado</div>
        <br />
        <div class="t-line">
          <span class="prompt">$</span>
          <span class="cmd">keel generate module users</span>
        </div>
        <div class="t-output">✓ modules/users/module.go</div>
        <div class="t-output">✓ modules/users/controller.go</div>
        <div class="t-output">✓ modules/users/service.go</div>
        <div class="t-output">✓ modules/users/repository.go</div>
        <br />
        <div class="t-line">
          <span class="prompt">$</span>
          <span class="cmd">keel generate crud products</span>
        </div>
        <div class="t-output">✓ CRUD completo generado</div>
        <div class="t-output">✓ DTOs, validaciones y rutas listas</div>
        <br />
        <div class="t-line">
          <span class="prompt">$</span>
          <span class="cmd">keel run</span>
        </div>
        <div class="t-output success">▶ Servidor corriendo en :3000</div>
        <div class="t-output success">▶ Docs en http://localhost:3000/docs</div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .cli-layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--dimensions-16, 64px);
    align-items: center;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    font-size: var(--text-sizes-sm, 14px);
    font-weight: var(--text-weights-medium, 500);
    color: var(--color-primary);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: var(--dimensions-4, 16px);
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 42px);
    font-weight: var(--text-weights-bold, 700);
    letter-spacing: -0.025em;
    line-height: var(--text-line-heights-tight, 1.2);
    margin-bottom: var(--dimensions-5, 20px);
    color: var(--ss-text);
  }

  .cli-desc {
    font-size: var(--text-sizes-base, 16px);
    color: var(--ss-muted);
    line-height: var(--text-line-heights-relaxed, 1.625);
    margin-bottom: var(--dimensions-6, 24px);
  }

  .cli-feature-list {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--dimensions-3, 12px);
    margin-bottom: var(--dimensions-8, 32px);
  }

  .cli-feature-list li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--dimensions-2, 8px);
    font-size: var(--text-sizes-sm, 14px);
    color: var(--ss-muted);
  }

  .cli-feature-list svg { color: #22c55e; flex-shrink: 0; }

  .cli-feature-list code {
    font-family: var(--text-fonts-mono, ui-monospace, monospace);
    font-size: 12px;
    background: var(--ss-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--ss-border);
    padding: 1px 6px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm, 4px);
  }

  .btn-cli {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 10px 20px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-base, 8px);
    font-size: var(--text-sizes-sm, 14px);
    font-weight: var(--text-weights-medium, 500);
    text-decoration: none;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-primary);
    color: var(--color-primary);
    transition: all var(--transitions-durations-short, 100ms);
  }

  .btn-cli:hover {
    background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.08);
  }

  /* ── Terminal ── */
  .terminal {
    background: #0d1117;
    border: 1px solid var(--ss-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg, 12px);
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
  }

  :global([data-theme="light"]) .terminal {
    border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
  }

  .terminal-bar {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    padding: 10px 14px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02);
  }

  .dot { width: 10px; height: 10px; border-radius: 50%; }
  .dot.red    { background: #ff5f57; }
  .dot.yellow { background: #febc2e; }
  .dot.green  { background: #28c840; }

  .terminal-title {
    margin-left: 6px;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: #94a3b8;
    font-family: var(--text-fonts-mono, ui-monospace, monospace);
  }

  .terminal-body {
    padding: 20px 24px;
    font-family: var(--text-fonts-mono, ui-monospace, monospace);
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .t-line {
    display: flex;
    gap: 10px;
  }

  .prompt { color: #4ade80; user-select: none; }
  .cmd    { color: #f1f5f9; }

  .t-output {
    color: #64748b;
    padding-left: 20px;
  }

  .t-output.success { color: #4ade80; }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .cli-layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .terminal { display: none; }
  }
</style>
